<div class="containter flex flex-col w-4/5 mx-auto my-8">
<div class="user-details">
  <%= render partial: 'users/user_info', locals: { user: @user } %>
  </div>
<div class="user-bio mx-auto my-8 flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-stone-600 rounded-xl border border-stone-700">
<h2 class="bio-heading mb-8 text-white"><%= t(:bio) %></h2>
  <p class="bio-text text-justify font-semibold text-white">
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. In odit laudantium maiores deleniti sequi id repudiandae
    perferendis. Odio molestias hic animi voluptate quae, maiores esse excepturi obcaecati illo totam minus!
    Labore velit veniam perferendis repellendus minima nostrum aliquam recusandae pariatur praesentium, quaerat sunt
    blanditiis suscipit delectus commodi nemo possimus? Aliquam, iste eum delectus nesciunt cum atque ex possimus
    expedita dicta assumenda quasi error earum reiciendis, numquam architecto! Velit molestiae eveniet tempore officiis
    quos voluptates temporibus adipisci ea quas sunt? Odit sunt doloremque labore atque culpa voluptate nemo qui, eveniet
    molestias neque dolorum aut provident eaque libero nostrum blanditiis optio. Minima aut fugit velit nulla inventore
    qui doloribus id vitae!
   </p>
  </div>

<div class="user-posts">
<% @user.posts.recent_posts(3).each do |post| %>
    <%= render partial: 'posts/post_item', locals: { post: post, user: @user } %>
  <% end %>

  <div class="see-all-posts mt-6 text-center">
<%= link_to t(:see_all_posts), user_posts_path(@user), class: "bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transform transition hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-600 focus:ring-opacity-50 hover:no-underline font-semibold" %>
  </div>
</div>

